{"id": "1405250483907592222", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "jenkins wants to invest in her 1 cost and her X cost the most!! A little bit of it involves how you prefer to play her, but I recommend prioritizing her 1 cost more, since you'll most likely be seeing it (and using it) more often, especially with her e1 scaling!", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T18:03:43.655000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405250853904060628", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "Teamwise she's pretty flexible, so as a dps character you'll want to be building around her. Your current team should actually work pretty well, but some other units you might want to consider swapping in or trying out in conjuction with her are Winkle, Castor (limited), or Lily (as a general ultra team shielder)", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T18:05:11.869000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405323809996800043", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "556812440239734784", "author_name": "_kumisan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "How do you set up her burst turn?\nDo you fill your ultra space with brown or x card for extra hit and brown?", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T22:55:05.957000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405326095125057637", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 19, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "I personally tend to set up my ultra space with brown first", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T23:04:10.774000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["556812440239734784"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1405323809996800043", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405326275371073748", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "And then on turns before you go in, if the enemy isn’t making any attacks and you have the x card in your hand as first playable, then you use it", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T23:04:53.748000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405326365162737845", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "Also remember to posse before using for extra arith esp if running rat posse", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T23:05:15.156000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405326525636804689", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "Aside from that, if you have a really big rat nuke card (9+ hits) I recommend actually saving it to put into ultra space the next turn", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T23:05:53.416000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405326574588395580", "channel_id": "1404957539992338442", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "So that the next ultra space turn you have a LOT of hits", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T23:06:05.087000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404957539992338442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Needing help on building Jenkin", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
