{"id": "1405273570833072259", "channel_id": "1405273570833072259", "type": 0, "author_id": "118966786497576962", "author_name": "mylieinapril11", "author_bot": false, "content": "hi there, new player here. ive been playing for a few days(just moved to chapter 3) and been looking at a lot of discords/reddit and I keep seeing everywhere how important dupes are in this game. is this true? its a bit of a struggle to want to pull new units to experience new gameplay but feeling like theyre not complete without more copies.", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T19:35:28.007000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405273570833072259", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "how important are dupes in this game?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545"]}
{"id": "1405278797011357867", "channel_id": "1405273570833072259", "type": 19, "author_id": "113374123798859776", "author_name": "legendaryredz", "author_bot": false, "content": "A lot of characters have key threshold (from E0 to E3) \nThe good thing is, as a F2P you have enough free pull currency to usually buy 1 character and either a dupe or a signature wheel every month\nAnd you get 1 free dupe selector per month for free", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T19:56:14.025000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["118966786497576962"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1405273570833072259", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405273570833072259", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "how important are dupes in this game?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545"]}
{"id": "1405279030952853614", "channel_id": "1405273570833072259", "type": 0, "author_id": "113374123798859776", "author_name": "legendaryredz", "author_bot": false, "content": "So the game can be dupe intensive but the F2P economy is built with it in mind and is fair even under those conditions", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T19:57:09.801000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405273570833072259", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "how important are dupes in this game?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545"]}
{"id": "1405279240697548891", "channel_id": "1405273570833072259", "type": 0, "author_id": "118966786497576962", "author_name": "mylieinapril11", "author_bot": false, "content": "gotcha ty, ill just keep that in mind and try to build teams I want to play instead of trying to get to many units at first", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T19:57:59.808000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405273570833072259", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "how important are dupes in this game?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545"]}
{"id": "1405017876309475339", "channel_id": "1405017876309475339", "type": 0, "author_id": "332427045701287939", "author_name": "ametikz", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello, just started playing yesterday and I like the game story, actually cried at Aigis arc, anyways, I got these units pulled up from numerous pulls on blue banner, just want to know if I should keep rolling or should I roll for wheels now? I got like 2 bulb item on inventory that allows me to get 2 ssr units, need some advice, tyia.", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T02:39:25.682000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1405017876636762122", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-08-13-09-52-52-213_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 227368, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1405017876309475339/1405017876636762122/Screenshot_2025-08-13-09-52-52-213_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2e1d&is=69cbdc9d&hm=e34f0cfad6629ee770baf9515b695e103832ba91a5de9d3eb3ff6d22a1847bd0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405017876309475339", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New player help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1405022516124057714", "channel_id": "1405017876309475339", "type": 0, "author_id": "857933985116061757", "author_name": "markiecart", "author_bot": false, "content": "You enter wheel jail once you got the main unit from the realm you are currently pulling at on their first dupe break point. Like in blue, its Caecus e3, Goliath e2. \n\nAfter that you can decide to move to other realm like Caro, Chaos, Ultra or enter the wheel jail to pull 1 titan blade and 1 incaculable. Then proceed to get 12 dupe of titan.", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T02:57:51.900000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405017876309475339", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New player help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
